# ✅ 🧠 Core Python Standard Library Modules

***

## 🔹 OS / System

```
os → OS operations (files, dirs, env)
sys → Python runtime (args, exit, path)
shutil → file operations (copy, move, delete)
pathlib → modern path handling
```

***

## 🔹 Process / Command Execution

```
subprocess → run Linux commands
signal → handle signals (kill, stop)
multiprocessing → parallel processing
threading → lightweight parallel tasks
```

***

## 🔹 File / Data Handling

```
open() → read/write files
json → JSON parsing
csv → CSV file handling
pickle → serialize objects
```

***

## 🔹 Date / Time

```
datetime → date & time handling
time → timestamps, sleep
```

***

## 🔹 Math / Numbers

```
math → basic math
random → random numbers
statistics → averages, mean
```

***

# ✅ 🌐 Networking / API Modules

***

## 🔹 HTTP / API

```
requests → REST API calls (GET/POST)
urllib → built-in HTTP client
http.client → low-level HTTP
```

***

## 🔹 Socket (Low-level networking)

```
socket → TCP/UDP communication
```

***

## 🔹 Email / Messaging

```
smtplib → send emails
imaplib → read emails
```

