# ✅ 🧠 How to remember ALL modules

Don’t try to memorize — use this pattern:

***

## ✅ Think in categories

| Task          | Module      |
| ------------- | ----------- |
| Run command   | subprocess  |
| File handling | os / shutil |
| API call      | requests    |
| Monitoring    | psutil      |
| Logging       | logging     |
| Cloud         | boto3       |
| Data          | pandas      |

***

# ✅ 🔥 Real DevOps Mapping (IMPORTANT)

***

| Linux command | Python module  |
| ------------- | -------------- |
| ls / cp       | os / shutil    |
| free          | psutil         |
| df            | psutil         |
| top           | psutil         |
| curl          | requests       |
| ssh           | paramiko       |
| cron          | sched / celery |

***

